* Genus ''[[Panthera]]'' 
** [[Leopard]], ''Panthera pardus'' (Aisia is Afraga)
** [[Leòmhann]], ''Panthera leo'' (Afraga, [[Coille Gir]] s[[na h-Innseachan]]; marbh ann an [[Eòrpa]],  [[Middle East]], a' mhòrchuid den Aisia, agus Aimearaga-a-Tuath)
** [[Iaguar]], ''Panthera onca'' ([[Na h-Aimearagan]]; bho [[Mexico]] gus an [[Argantain]]-a-tuath)
** [[Tigear]], ''Panthera tigris'' (Aisia) 
* Genus ''Acinonyx''
** [[Sìotà]], ''Acinonyx jubatus'' (Afraga agus [[Ioran]])
* Genus ''[[Puma (genus)|Puma]]''
** [[Pùma]], ''Puma concolor'' ([[Na h-Aimearagan]])
* Genus ''Uncia''
** [[Leopard-sneachda]], ''Uncia uncia'' (beinntean ann am [[Meadhon Aisia|meadhoin]] agus [[Aisia-a-Deas|taobh-a-deas]] [[Aisia]])

